{"type":null,"faqId":11388,"title":"Mate2 (MT2-L05)  如何启用屏幕解锁图案？","answer":"<p style=\"margin-left:63.25pt;text-indent:-12.2pt;\">\n\t<span style=\"font-family:Wingdings;\">l<span style=\"font-size:7pt;line-height:normal;font-family:'Times New Roman';\"> </span></span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;\">点击</span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;\"> </span><b><span style=\"font-family:&quot;\">设置</span></b><span style=\"font-family:&quot;\"> &gt;<b> </b></span><b><span style=\"font-family:&quot;\">安全</span></b><span style=\"font-family:&quot;\"> &gt; </span><b><span style=\"font-family:&quot;\">屏幕锁定</span></b><span style=\"font-family:&quot;\"> &gt; </span><b><span style=\"font-family:&quot;\">图案</span></b><span style=\"font-family:&quot;\">。</span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;\"></span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"margin-left:63.25pt;text-indent:-12.2pt;\">\n\t<span style=\"font-family:Wingdings;\">l<span style=\"font-size:7pt;line-height:normal;font-family:'Times New Roman';\"> </span></span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;\">在</span><b><span style=\"font-family:&quot;\">“</span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:&quot;\">选择您的图案</span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:&quot;\">”</span></b><span style=\"font-family:&quot;\">界面，通过手指在屏幕连续划过几个圆的圆心设定解锁时使用的图形样式，再点击</span><b><span style=\"font-family:&quot;\">“</span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:&quot;\">继续</span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:&quot;\">”</span></b><span style=\"font-family:&quot;\">。</span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;\"></span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"margin-left:63.25pt;text-indent:-12.2pt;\">\n\t<span style=\"font-family:Wingdings;\">l<span style=\"font-size:7pt;line-height:normal;font-family:'Times New Roman';\"> </span></span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;\">再次在屏幕上划过刚才的样式，点击</span><b><span style=\"font-family:&quot;\">“</span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:&quot;\">确认</span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:&quot;\">”</span></b><span style=\"font-family:&quot;\">完成解锁图形的设置。</span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;\"></span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"margin-left:63.25pt;text-indent:-12.2pt;\">\n\t<span style=\"font-family:Wingdings;\">l<span style=\"font-size:7pt;line-height:normal;font-family:'Times New Roman';\"> </span></span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;\">当点电源键或开关机时，手机会默认进入图案解锁界面，在该界面划过刚才的图案样式，进行解锁。</span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;\"></span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"margin-left:63.25pt;text-indent:-12.2pt;\">\n\t<span style=\"font-family:&quot;\"><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=32410\" alt=\"\" /><br />\n</span> \n</p>","faqTypeId":143,"faqType":"系统功能与设置","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"2145","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-System-Settings","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1398225215000,"seriesProductName":"MT2-L05","visitedTimes":28,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"Mate2 (MT2-L05)","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}